description:
Features

The Caravana GT Styling Tape-On RV Window Deflector RainBlade is designed to enhance your camper's functionality and style. It features a sleek, aerodynamic design that effectively deflects rain, wind, and debris away from your windows.

  • Tape-on Installation: Effortlessly apply the deflector to your RV window with the included adhesive backing. No drilling or special tools required.
  • Durable Construction: Crafted from high-quality materials, this deflector is built to withstand the rigors of road travel and weather conditions.
  • Wind & Rain Deflection: The aerodynamic design redirects wind and rain away from your windows, creating a more comfortable and enjoyable driving experience.
  • Improved Visibility: By keeping your windows clear of debris and moisture, you can maintain optimal visibility while on the road.

Specifications

This window deflector is designed to fit a wide range of RV windows. The specific dimensions will be provided with the product packaging.

Benefits

The Caravana GT Styling Tape-On RV Window Deflector RainBlade offers numerous benefits for RV enthusiasts:

  • Reduced Wind Noise: By effectively deflecting wind, this deflector helps minimize unwanted noise inside your camper.
  • Enhanced Comfort: Enjoy a more comfortable driving experience with reduced rain and wind intrusion.
  • Improved Window Protection: Shield your windows from scratches, dirt, and other potential damage caused by road debris.

Usage

Installing the Caravana GT Styling Tape-On RV Window Deflector RainBlade is simple and straightforward:

  1. Clean the window surface thoroughly with soap and water. Ensure it is completely dry before proceeding.
  2. Peel off the protective backing from the adhesive tape on the deflector.
  3. Carefully align the deflector with the top edge of your RV window and press firmly to secure it in place.

You can enjoy a clear view and a more comfortable driving experience after installation. For optimal performance, avoid washing or cleaning your windows immediately after installation. Allow the adhesive to fully cure for at least 24 hours before exposing it to water.

description:
Features

This Caravan Filter Water Tank Filling Pre-Filter is designed to ensure clean and safe water for your RV adventures. It features a gravity-fill design, making it easy to connect to your external water source. The pre-filter effectively removes impurities from the incoming water supply, protecting your RV's plumbing system and providing you with pure drinking water.

  • Gravity-fill Design: Effortlessly fill your RV's water tank by simply connecting the pre-filter to an external water source. Water flows through the filter by gravity, eliminating the need for pumps or manual operation.
  • Effective Impurity Removal:
    • The pre-filter utilizes a high-quality filtration system to trap dirt, debris, sediment, and other contaminants from your water supply, safeguarding your RV's plumbing and providing cleaner drinking water.

Specifications

This Caravan Filter Water Tank Filling Pre-Filter is constructed with durable materials and designed for reliable performance. Its compact size makes it easy to store and transport.

Benefits

By using this pre-filter, you'll enjoy several key benefits:

  • Protection for Your RV's Plumbing System: The pre-filter acts as a barrier, preventing harmful impurities from entering your RV's water lines and potentially causing damage.
  • Improved Water Quality: Enjoy cleaner, safer drinking water by removing contaminants that can affect taste and odor.
  • Peace of Mind While Traveling: Knowing your water is clean and safe will give you peace of mind during your RV adventures.

Usage

Using the Caravan Filter Water Tank Filling Pre-Filter is straightforward:

  1. Connect the pre-filter to an external water source, such as a campground spigot.
  2. Attach the other end of the pre-filter to your RV's water tank inlet.
  3. Allow gravity to fill your water tank. The pre-filter will automatically remove impurities from the water supply.

For optimal performance, periodically inspect and clean the pre-filter according to the manufacturer's instructions.

  • Effective pre-filtration eliminates sediment, dirt, and other impurities that can contaminate your fresh water tank.
  • Durable construction designed to withstand the rigors of RV life.

Experience the freedom of clean, reliable water wherever your travels take you. Upgrade your caravan with this essential pre-filter system today!

titre: 60cmx5m RV Radiator Heat Reflective Insulating Foil Energy Saving Radiator Pad Panel Motorhome Caravan Interior Accessories
description:
Features

This reflective insulating foil is designed specifically for use in RVs, motorhomes, and caravans to help regulate heat and conserve energy.

  • Reflective surface: Effectively reflects radiant heat back towards the radiator, maximizing heating efficiency.
  • Easy installation: The flexible foil can be easily cut and shaped to fit your RV's radiator area.
  • Durable construction: Made from a high-quality material that is designed to withstand repeated use and temperature fluctuations.

Specifications

Dimensions: 60cm x 5m

Material: Reflective insulating foil

Benefits

By reflecting heat back towards the radiator, this insulating foil helps to improve heating efficiency and reduce energy consumption. This can lead to significant cost savings on your fuel bills, especially during cold weather.

The reflective insulation also helps to create a more comfortable living environment by reducing heat loss through the walls of your RV. In addition, it can help to prevent condensation from forming, which can contribute to mold and mildew growth.

Usage

To use this radiator heat reflective insulating foil, simply cut it to the desired size and shape to fit behind your RV's radiator. The adhesive backing will allow you to securely attach it to the wall or surface.

Ensure that the reflective side of the foil faces towards the radiator for optimal performance. For best results, install the foil before winter arrives to maximize its benefits during the coldest months.

This product is an effective and easy way to improve your RV's heating efficiency, reduce energy costs, and create a more comfortable living environment.
name: 60cm x 5m RV Radiator Reflective Insulation Foil Heat Saving Panel for Motorhomes & Caravans

  • Reflective Foil Technology: Traps radiant heat and minimizes energy loss for greater efficiency.
  • Durable Construction: Built to withstand the rigors of RV life.
  • Easy Installation: Simply place the pad behind your radiator for quick and hassle-free application.
  • Versatile Size: The 60cm x 5m dimensions provide ample coverage for most RV radiators.

Save money on heating costs and enjoy a more comfortable living space in your motorhome or caravan. This essential accessory is a must-have for anyone seeking increased warmth and energy savings.
